WEBVTT

00:00:29.546 --> 00:00:30.717
But this is different.

00:00:30.741 --> 00:00:34.420
This is coming from the heart of finance.

00:00:34.444 --> 00:00:37.344
The first quote
is from Jean-Claude Trichet

00:00:37.368 --> 00:00:40.230
when he was governor
of the European Central Bank.

00:00:41.180 --> 00:00:45.920
The second quote is from the head
of the UK Financial Services Authority.

00:00:47.015 --> 00:00:48.562
Are these people implying

00:00:48.586 --> 00:00:51.326
that we don't understand
the economic systems

00:00:51.350 --> 00:00:53.689
that drive our modern societies?

00:00:54.519 --> 00:00:55.669
It gets worse.

